title: The Flash | 2.9
description:
Noah and Sara find themselves inside a spaceship. They're trapped and they must quickly decide whether to make enemies or allies of two scientists working for The Collective. One false move could be deadly.
CAST
Narrator – Mike Howorun
Noah – Brady Roberts
Sara – Greta Carew-Johns
Terry – Kevin Doree
Female Scientist – Jelena Milinkovic
Captain – Steve Sauve
Arthur – Andrew Chornohus
Boudreau – Matthew Hall
Andres – Roland Ruiz
Editing and Sound Design – Matthew Hall & Mike Howorun
Post Production Producer - Rob Johnston
Written/Directed – Mike Howorun
Produced by - Matthew Hall, Brady Roberts, Mike Howorun, Dila Velázquez
Created by Mike Howorun & Brady Roberts
